{"data":[{"id":563024788,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e065cc93278328f28538711740554d09","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563024788","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546174033,"updated_time":1546174033,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":26,"content":"\u003cp\u003e知乎对套路见得太少了，真正是网络社区的鄙视链下游。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这种帖子（提问）放到民科吧，一会就沉下去了，在知乎上竟然能有上万关注，提问者一瞬间多了两万多粉丝。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下面的人还在各种论证分析……分析个啥啊。凤姐/芙蓉姐姐的套路换个包装你们就不认识了吗。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560661653,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560661653","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877651,"updated_time":1545877651,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":12,"content":"\u003cp\u003e没有想到这个问题引起了不少关注，甚至不少回答者做出了各色各样的回答，当然无论嘲讽，讥笑，批判，鼓励，原本以为只是个脑洞题，没想到确实是有人真实的内心问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我无法就这个问题给出回答，但是可以反过来给予一定的思考:进入清华北大，数学方面就能做出巨大的成就吗，答案自然是否定的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今年刚好是中科院20周年庆，科院回顾了相关领域的成果，摘取部分如下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e席南华对仿射A型Weyl群证明了Lusztig关于基环的猜想，成为国际上很多后续工作的基础之一\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e周向宇带领研究生解决了多复变中的“经典问题”最优L2延拓问题、证明了Demailly强开性猜想，在美国《数学评论》上被评论为“近年来多复变与代数几何领域最伟大的成就之一”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“新生代”数学家田野首次给出7个千禧数学问题之一“椭圆曲线BSD猜想”的重要线索\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e人称“论证骑士”的孙斌勇与李文威对朗兰兹纲领一系列重要问题的探索，以及青年学者黄飞敏在玻尔兹曼方程的流体力学方面，都取得了重要的突破\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e冯康独立于西方创始了有限元方法，在国际上首次提出基于辛几何原理计算哈密尔顿体系的新方法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e袁亚湘等最早使用子空间技术分析计算方法，相继提出了子空间共轭梯度法、非线性优化子空间法与子空间拟牛顿法等方法。该方法被称为Dai-Yuan方法，并且与FR方法、HS方法、PRP方法并列，被认为是“四个主要方法”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e张平和黄飞敏团队证明了各向异性不可压缩Navier-Stokes方程整体适定性；证明了在黎曼解这一重要情形下Boltzmann方程的极限是可压缩Euler方程\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e插一个故事（我听彭实戈讲过一个故事:他高中的时候正好哥猜流行，他的许多同学那时候也兴致勃勃，想要在这方面一展身手，但大多数后来就放弃了，后来他知识青年下乡，经常捧着一本苏联某数学课本看，周围没有几个懂数学的，不会的问题经常是跑几个村子去找能够解答的人讨论）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e观看他们的履历不难发现，绝大多数不是清北出身，当然北大出身自然也有做出了很多巨大成就的，但是无一例外不是在各自领域深耕数十年，现代数学的庞杂性远超过很多人的理解，提及数学绝不是只有哥猜甚至是囿于基础数学领域，大概率的结果是对于非基础数学领域的其他数学工作者，相关领域的突破要比哥猜来的重要些。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真要证明自己的价值，不是非要攀登数学的几座顶峰，那上面容易缺氧窒息而亡，不如先爬几座山头，锻炼一下身体，在决定是否要那些方向走。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561411006,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bbf04340aef5809fbe75adc27a19e46d","url_token":"xin-zhao-de-shui-li-bo-shi","name":"赜实先生","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f9cc23903f4fda215a6e0653d170fec3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f9cc23903f4fda215a6e0653d170fec3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bbf04340aef5809fbe75adc27a19e46d","user_type":"people","headline":"B站up主赜实先生，视频主页：\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//space.bilibili.com/349475422\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003espace.bilibili.com/3494\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e75422\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561411006","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4d83bf0e7d02de2687d11bf078fd9a1c_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545965657,"updated_time":1545965894,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如何看待高中生几个月前还在研究错位相减法，\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/search?q=%E6%B4%9B%E5%BF%85%E8%BE%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%88%99\u0026amp;source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_extra=%7B%22sourceType%22%3A%22answer%22%2C%22sourceId%22%3A561363306%7D\" class=\"internal\"\u003e洛必达法则\u003c/a\u003e，导数，隐函数，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e几个月后就声称自己证明了哥德巴赫猜想?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e2a4fc4123919f56773e2c9e55796577_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d485d2f2ca179a1514710b421248660c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e2a4fc4123919f56773e2c9e55796577_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2248'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-